column5: If anyone is interested Little Lake in Barrie is now ice free.
Drive by everyday.  Is was 75% open.  All the ice was pushed over to the east shoreline.
Can you get to the store yet?
by boat you can...lol  I don't really know if the water has dropped or not
I didn't get off the 400..  But the water looked pretty high..
Tube,n for crappies soon. Warm up water.
Water looks to be quite high.
It's good the water levels are high... they've been far too low last couple years there from I believe the golf courses tapping in to it.
